TextEng: Err... hello there. Everything all right?
Text: 어... 안녕하세요. 괜찮으신가요?

TextEng: Aye, be safe!
Text: 네, 조심하세요!

TextEng: Be careful on those streets. They'll kill you if you're spotted.
Text: 거리에서 조심하세요. 들키면 죽습니다.

TextEng: Aye, go, go!
Text: 네, 어서, 어서요!

TextEng: I see. A little on the slow side, are we? No matter, I guess.
Text: 그렇군요. 좀 느리신 편인가요? 뭐, 상관없겠지만.

TextEng: Questions? What do you want to know?
Text: 질문요? 뭘 알고 싶으신데요?

TextEng: I... suppose so.
Text: 저... 그런 것 같아요.

TextEng: Err... aye. I can... answer a question.
Text: 어... 네. 질문에... 답할 수는 있어요.

TextEng: Back again? Did you... need something?
Text: 또 오셨어요? 뭔가... 필요하신 거예요?

TextEng: Uh... what... what do you want?
Text: 어... 뭘... 원하시는 거예요?

TextEng: I... uh, sure...
Oh! You... you don't want to stay here! P-please! There's... there's the Cutlass Inn. It's to the left of the main gate... they says it's still open.
Text: 아! 당신은... 여기 있으면 안 돼요! 제, 제발요! 저기... 커틀러스 여관이 있어요. 정문 왼쪽에... 아직 영업 중이래요.

TextEng: There weren't many. Tyr has a temple, on the west side...
Text: 많지 않았어요. 티르 신전이 있어요, 서쪽에...

TextEng: Most of the stores are gone, or empty. I don't know.
Text: 대부분의 가게가 없어졌거나 비어 있어요. 모르겠어요.

TextEng: Uhh... there's Miss Bela's. That's a brothel, if you're... well... if you want to know. It's across from the gate. Not sure what else you'd want to see...
Text: 어... 벨라 아가씨네가 있어요. 거긴 창관이에요, 혹시... 뭐... 알고 싶으시다면요. 정문 건너편에 있어요. 다른 뭘 보고 싶으실지는 모르겠지만...

TextEng: Did... you want something else?
Text: 다른... 원하시는 게 있으세요?

TextEng: Ahhh! Not again! Leave me alone!!
Text: 으악! 또야! 날 내버려 둬요!!

TextEng: Don't hurt me! Please don't hurt me!!
Text: 때리지 마요! 제발 때리지 마요!!

TextEng: Someone help me! Please, for the love of the gods!!
Text: 누가 도와줘요! 제발, 신이시여!!

TextEng: Please! You... you don't look like them soldiers... you won't hurt me, will you?
Text: 제발요! 당신은... 그 군인들처럼 안 생겼어요... 저 안 때리시죠?

TextEng: Ahhh! Don't... don't hurt me! Haven't we had enough?!
Text: 으악! 때리지... 때리지 마요! 이만하면 됐잖아요?!

TextEng: Aiiieee!! Don't kill me! I don't want to die!!
Text: 아이고!! 죽이지 마요! 죽기 싫어요!!

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Success]</Start> I... suppose you don't seem the bad sort. You just startled me so! With all the soldiers rampaging around, I assumed...
Text: <StartCheck>[성공]</Start> 저... 나쁜 사람은 아닌 것 같네요. 너무 놀라서요! 군인들이 날뛰고 있으니까, 당연히...

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Failure]</Start> I don't believe you! You're just like the other soldiers, you are!! Here to rob me or kill me!!
Text: <StartCheck>[실패]</Start> 못 믿겠어요! 당신도 다른 군인들이랑 똑같아요!! 날 털거나 죽이러 온 거잖아요!!

TextEng: Aahhh! Robber!! Get away, get away!!
Text: 으악! 도둑이야!! 저리 가, 저리 가요!!

TextEng: Thank Ilmater! Just go, go!!
Text: 일메이터께 감사드려요! 어서 가요, 가!!

TextEng: Well... what did you want from me? Why are you here?
Text: 그럼... 저한테 뭘 원하시는 거예요? 왜 여기 오신 거예요?

TextEng: I... I know. It's just that the soldiers have been rampaging through the streets for weeks, now...
Text: 저... 알아요. 그냥 군인들이 몇 주째 거리를 휩쓸고 있어서...

TextEng: They take whatever they like. If they think you can fight, they force you to join one of the High Captains' armies... or they kill you.
Text: 원하는 건 다 빼앗아요. 싸울 수 있다고 생각하면 대선장 군대에 강제로 끌고 가고... 아니면 죽여요.

TextEng: And... and the gods forbid that they think you're working for one of the other High Captains...
Text: 그리고... 만약 다른 대선장 밑에서 일한다고 생각하면... 끔찍해요...

TextEng: N-nobody knows, for sure. Some weeks ago, the High Captains just started... started trying to kill each other.
Text: 아, 아무도 확실히 몰라요. 몇 주 전에 대선장들이 갑자기... 서로 죽이려고 하기 시작했어요.

TextEng: Each one of them has their own army, and they've been fighting in the streets night and day. Buildings burned, people slaughtered... everything's falling apart!
Text: 각자 군대를 갖고 있고, 밤낮으로 거리에서 싸워요. 건물이 불타고, 사람들이 학살당하고... 모든 게 무너지고 있어요!

TextEng: Worse, now that so many are dead... there's monsters come to the streets. Big rats and walking dead. Some says the High Captains use them for their armies, too.
Text: 더 나쁜 건, 죽은 사람이 많아서... 거리에 괴물들이 나타났어요. 큰 쥐랑 걸어 다니는 시체들이요. 대선장들이 군대에 쓴다는 소문도 있어요.

TextEng: I don't... know much about them. There was five of them, and they is all pirate lords, or used t' be. They've gone mad, everyone says.
Text: 잘... 몰라요. 다섯 명이 있었고, 전부 해적 영주였어요, 아니면 예전에 그랬거나. 다들 미쳤다고 해요.

TextEng: Maybe each of them wants to control the city, I don't know... but they're killing everyone and they don't care what happens to any of us.
Text: 아마 각자 도시를 지배하고 싶은 거겠죠, 모르겠어요... 하지만 모든 사람을 죽이고 있고 우리한테 무슨 일이 생기든 신경 안 써요.

TextEng: N-no... who? Maybe the wizards, I don't know.
Text: 아, 아뇨... 누가요? 아마 마법사들, 모르겠어요.

TextEng: The wizards of that Arcane Brotherhood. They lives in a big tower on the island at the mouth of the river.
Text: 비전 결사단 마법사들이요. 강 어귀 섬에 있는 큰 탑에 살아요.

TextEng: I don't know any more abouts them, I swear! They... they're just supposed to be real powerful, that's all.
Text: 그들에 대해 더 아는 거 없어요, 맹세해요! 그들이... 정말 강력하다는 것만 알아요, 그게 다예요.
